---
title: Circuit Breaker — Toestandsdiagram (BookingComAdapter)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> CLOSED

    CLOSED: CLOSED
    CLOSED: Requests gaan door
    CLOSED: failureCount = 0

    OPEN: OPEN
    OPEN: Requests direct geblokkeerd
    OPEN: (fail fast — geen call naar provider)

    HALF_OPEN: HALF_OPEN
    HALF_OPEN: Eén proberequest toegestaan
    HALF_OPEN: verdere requests geblokkeerd

    CLOSED --> OPEN: failureCount ≥ 3<br/>(drempel bereikt)
    OPEN --> HALF_OPEN: na 15s<br/>(recoveryTimeout verstreken)
    HALF_OPEN --> CLOSED: probe slaagt<br/>recordSuccess()
    HALF_OPEN --> OPEN: probe faalt<br/>recordFailure()
    CLOSED --> CLOSED: succes<br/>failureCount = 0

    note right of CLOSED
        Normale werking.
        Elke fout verhoogt failureCount.
    end note

    note right of OPEN
        Fail fast — bespaart de provider
        én het eigen latency-budget.
    end note

    note right of HALF_OPEN
        Voorzichtige hersteltest
        zonder volledige belasting.
    end note
